text: Kristal Melisa Marshall (born November 11, 1983) is an American model, beauty queen and former professional wrestler. She is best known for her time in World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE) on their SmackDown brand, and in Total Nonstop Action Wrestling (TNA). She was part of the 2005 WWE Diva Search. ==Personal life== Marshall dated Bobby Lashley from 2007 until 2010, and they have two children. In April 2010, Marshall confirmed on Twitter that she and Lashley had split.
